# Pew dbt test YAML overlay

Extends [agent-test-yaml](agent-test-yaml.mdc) for Pew Digital Data Mart (`ddm-dbt`).

## Pew test patterns

- `not_null` / `unique` on natural keys — `severity: warn` for legacy tables
- `relationships` for FK integrity — `severity: warn`; known orphans documented in audit
- Singular tests in `tests/singular/` for business invariants
- Known pre-existing warnings: `docs/dbt_assessment_audit.md` "Known test warnings" section

## Pew grain / key context

- Content marts: composite keys often include `sitecore_item_id` + date — see `ga4-metrics.mdc`
- Conventions: `dbt-conventions.mdc`
